				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "The player witnesses an invasive parasite emerge from a dead body - the very same kind of parasite that currently resides inside them. They try to kill it, but find this curiously difficult - the little creature can psychically influence the player and tries to sway them from doing it harm. Meanwhile, Daisy encourages us to harvest it to absorb its potential. "
